<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink56-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">purattoḻukkam uḷatākiyataṟintu talaimakaḷ melintuḻi, ‘aḵtillai’ eṉṟu tēṟṟum talaimakaṟkut tōḻi colliyatu.
      </p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink56">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>pakalkoḷ viḷakkō ṭirānā ḷaṟiyā</l>
<l>velpōrc cōḻa ṉāmū raṉṉaviva</l>
<l>ṇalampeṟu cuṭarnuta ṟēmpa</l>
<l>vevaṉpayañ ceyyunī tēṟṟiya moḻiyē.</l>
</lg>

<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">


<l>   The girl who is like Āmūr </l> 
<l rend="indent2"> [that city] of the Cōḻa kings, victorious in battle,</l> 
<l rend="indent2"> where one cannot tell day from night</l> 
<l rend="indent2">            thanks to lamps that turn night into day – </l> 
<l> What is the use of your explanations, </l> 
<l rend="indent2"> now that her [once] glowing and beautiful brow is growing dim? </l> 


  
  
  
  </lg>
    </div>
